Articles.Content:
@regex

A post like that is exactly what I was thinking Squad needs to write to help clear everything up. With the game now in experimentals, Squad is going to be extra busy on top of their normal reticence to discuss these issues so I'm not really expecting to hear anything from Squad, at least not until after the game releases. Hopefully at that point the devs will be more willing to talk about things after a post-release vacation.

At this point, despite my disagreements with Squad's decisions and my resulting posts voicing my concerns (and sometimes with a little criticism), I'm really hoping for an excellent release. I want to be proven wrong and shown that my concerns were unfounded, above all I really just want to play an amazing version of KSP.
